It’s not just a lip combo.
It’s a mood reset. A power move. A reminder that you still care — about showing up, even on the messy days. 💄✨

#SoftPower #MainCharacterEnergy #BeautyInTheDetails

Not blending in. Never was the plan.
Somewhere along the way, we were told that to be taken seriously, we had to blend in.
Wear the greys. Play it safe. Tuck our personalities away to “look professional.”

But here’s the thing — I’ve never felt more powerful than when I showed up as myself.

Bold, curious, a little playful — and yes, dressed like I mean it.

This is me, letting go of the propaganda.
And building something better.

#PropagandaImNotFallingFor #MadeToMatter #OLKA #RewriteTheRules #WomenInBusiness
